keyFacts: The document is an email from Judge Alison J. Nathan's chambers regarding case 20cr330, US v. Maxwell.
An order was issued by Judge Nathan on November 11, 2021, and was being forwarded to counsel on November 12, 2021.
The order was scheduled to be filed on the court docket on the morning following the email.
